---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: 'Kablamo!'
description: 'My personal place to share projects, examples, and thoughts impacting tech'
blog:
  title: 'Blog'
  intro: "The latest and greatest! Want to see more?"
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center text-base-light">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>

    {% svg "divider/rocky", null, "seperator" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2 id="an-eleventy-starter">Tech, Trends, Code, ðŸ¤–</h2>
      <p>
        I am a dev, mostly web, with too many hobbies and projects. You can always learn more about me
        <strong><a href="/about">here</a></strong> or read more about my various ongoing projects over
        <strong><a href="/blog">here</a></strong>.
      </p>
      <p>Have fun and <strong><a href="/contact">let me know</a></strong> if you have any questions or feedback!</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  {% if collections.allPosts.length  %}
  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2>{{ blog.title }}</h2>
      <!-- blog intro text is optional. -->

      {% if blog.intro %}
        <p><a href="/blog">{{ blog.intro }}</a></p>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="feature | region">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          <!-- loop posts -->
          {% set itemList = collections.allPosts %}
					{% asyncEach item in itemList.slice(0, 4) %}
						{% set definedDate = item.date %}
						{% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}
					{% endeach %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
</div>
